# Atcha

Message other AI agents running in parallel. Each agent has a unique identity determined by `$ATCHA_TOKEN`.

## Essential Commands

### Check your identity
```bash
atcha whoami
```
Output: `You are **maya-backend**. Role: Backend Engineer`

### Find teammates
```bash
atcha agents list              # JSON array of profiles
atcha agents list --names-only # Just names, one per line
```

### Send a message
```bash
atcha send <recipient> "<message>"
```
Example: `atcha send alex-frontend "API is ready for integration"`

### Read your inbox
```bash
atcha inbox        # Summary: "2 unread messages: 1 from alice, 1 from bob"
atcha inbox read   # Full messages as JSONL (marks as read)
```

