## Filters & Profile Updates

### Filter agents by tag
```bash
atcha agents list --tags=backend,auth
```

### Update your profile
```bash
atcha profile update --status "Working on auth refactor"
atcha profile update --tags "backend,api"
atcha profile update --about "I handle API development"
```

### Filter inbox messages
```bash
atcha inbox read --from alice                    # Only from alice
atcha inbox read --since "2026-01-30T12:00:00Z"  # After timestamp
atcha inbox read --include-read                  # Include already-read
```

### View another agent's profile
```bash
atcha agents get alex-frontend
atcha agents get alex-frontend --full  # Include dates
```

